    "115238769": {
      "title": "About damping of hydromagnetic waves in a turbulent plasma",
      "abstract": "Translated from Geomagn. Aeron.; 13: No. 2, 311-317(1973). The damping decrement of hydromagnetic waves is evaluated in a weakly turbulent plasma in the case of high and low frequencies (in comparison with the reciprocal time of isotropization of the pulsation spectrum). The basis used for the approach is ionacoustic turbulence. (auth)"
